OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,FBelfast International Airport has been
OL,8,Fforced to apologise to a woman with a
OL,9,Fstoma who was asked to lift her dress
OL,10,Fnot once but twice, as she went
OL,11,Fthrough security.
OL,13,FClaire McCorry has had a stoma since
OL,14,Fshe was a child and travelled
OL,15,Fextensively during her career but says
OL,16,Fher stoma has only been an issue at
OL,17,FBelfast International Airport.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
