OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,FClaire decided to share her experience
OL,8,Fafter UTV reported on a similar
OL,9,Fincident involving another woman
OL,10,Fearlier this month.
OL,12,FFirst experiencing the issue while
OL,13,Fpassing through security in July last
OL,14,Fyear, Claire said the issue reoccured
OL,15,Fin October.
OL,17,FShe described being taken to an area
OL,18,Flike a store room to carry out the
OL,19,Fsearch.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
