OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,FSpeaking of the experience she said:
OL,8,F"They had already patted me down and
OL,9,FI'd said, look, I have a stoma, you're
OL,10,Fgoing to feel it.
OL,12,F"Then, after patting me down, said
OL,13,Fwell, we need to see it. I initially
OL,14,Fwas so gobsmacked because it's never
OL,15,Fhappened to me before.
OL,17,F"I went, no, no, it just felt so
OL,18,Fludicrous to me... and at that point I
OL,19,Fjust had to lift my dress.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
