OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,F"I knew I wasn't going to fly unless I
OL,8,Flifted my dress. So I was so
OL,9,Fdistraught, I actually cried for the
OL,10,Fentire time."
OL,12,FJust a few months later in October,
OL,13,Fthe same incident occurred.
OL,15,F"This time I was wearing jeans and a
OL,16,Ftop, and they asked, could they lift
OL,17,Fit. And I said, well, you can search
OL,18,Fme, but if you can do it without
OL,19,Flifting the top.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
