OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1753965208
OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,F"So she wasn't happy with it, so she
OL,8,Ftook me off again."
OL,10,FClaire wanted to speak up on behalf of
OL,11,Fthose with a stoma, so the incident
OL,12,Fdoesn't happen again.
OL,14,F"I've had my stoma when I was 12, but
OL,15,Fthere are people who are just coming
OL,16,Fto terms with it, and I do know people
OL,17,Fwho don't want to fly because they're
OL,18,Fafraid of this type of thing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
