OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,F"When I seen Rhonda's story it really
OL,8,Fupset me again because it brought me
OL,9,Fback, but I was so angry because I
OL,10,Ffeel they've learned nothing."
OL,12,FIn a statement Belfast International
OL,13,FAirport said: "We regret that any of
OL,14,Four passengers have had an upsetting
OL,15,Fexperience while travelling through
OL,16,FBelfast International Airport.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
