OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,F"We remain fully committed to ensuring
OL,8,Fall passengers can travel with comfort
OL,9,Fand dignity through the airport and
OL,10,Fwill continue to regularly review our
OL,11,Fprocedures and enhance staff training
OL,12,Faround managing sensitive situations.
OL,14,F"The UK Department For Transport (DfT)
OL,15,Fis responsible for setting the policy
OL,16,Ffor aviation security for all UK
OL,17,FAirports with advice from the Civil
OL,18,FAviation Authority.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
