OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,F"It is a legal requirement that all
OL,8,Fpassengers, including those wearing
OL,9,Fstoma bags or medical devices, are
OL,10,Fsubject to security screening and we
OL,11,Ffully comply with those regulations
OL,12,Fand procedures.
OL,14,F"On average every month at Belfast
OL,15,FInternational Airport we provide
OL,16,Fspecial assistance to over 12,000
OL,17,Fpassengers with physical and hidden
OL,18,Fdisabilities.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
