OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,F"Our Accessibility Forum is comprised
OL,8,Fof many different organisations who
OL,9,Frepresent those passengers who require
OL,10,Fspecial assistance, and we have a
OL,11,Fcommunity stoma nurse and a
OL,12,Frepresentative of the Urostomy
OL,13,FAssociation on that forum who
OL,14,Fregularly provide us with information
OL,15,Fand suggestions to improve the
OL,16,Fpassenger process and experience.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
