OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,F"Our security provider, Wilson James,
OL,8,Falso have a dedicated programme of
OL,9,Fongoing disability training for our
OL,10,Fsecurity teams including stoma
OL,11,Fawareness training.
OL,13,F"In August 2024 Belfast International
OL,14,FAirport implemented Next Generation
OL,15,FScreening Technology as directed by
OL,16,Fthe UK Government DFT for all UK
OL,17,FAirports.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
