OL,3,CWoman with stoma asked on two
OL,4,Coccasions to lift dress at airport
OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,F"These new scanners can allow
OL,8,Fpassengers to leave liquids and
OL,9,Felectronics in their hand luggage
OL,10,Fwhile all passengers, including
OL,11,Fdisabled passengers and those with
OL,12,Fhidden disabilities, pass through a
OL,13,Fbody scanner; unless they ask for or
OL,14,Fare offered an alternative screening
OL,15,Fprocess.
OL,17,F"Due to the nature of this technology,
OL,18,Fwhile it reduces the instances where a
OL,19,Ffull hand search of passengers is
OL,20,Frequired,
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
