OL,5,Csecurity
OL,7,F"It also means some passengers,
OL,8,Fincluding those with hidden
OL,9,Fdisabilities, may set off an alarm
OL,10,Fwhich the security officer must
OL,11,Faddress.
OL,13,F"Regarding CCTV- this is in place for
OL,14,Fthe safety and security of passengers
OL,15,Fand staff and is disposed of in line
OL,16,Fwith GDPR procedures."
